<h1 id=3D"Requirements-serverServer"><span class=3D"confluence-anchor-link"=
 id=3D"Requirements-server"></span>Server</h1>
<p>eZ software is built to rely on existing technologies and standards. The=
 minimal&nbsp;setup is&nbsp;<code>PHP</code>, &nbsp;<code>MySQL/MariaDB</co=
de>, and <code>Apache/Nginx</code>. Recommendation for production setups is=
 to use Varnish, and &nbsp;<code>Memcached</code>, <code>NFS<span style=3D"=
font-family: Arial , sans-serif;">&nbsp;and&nbsp;</span></code><code>Solr</=
code> in a <a href=3D"/display/TECHDOC/Clustering">clustered</a> setup.</p>
<p><span>For supported versions of these technologies see Recommended and S=
upported setups below.</span></p>
<h2 id=3D"Requirements-Recommendedsetups">Recommended setups</h2>
<p>These setups are tested by QA and are generally recommended setups. For =
security and performance we furthermore recommend use of the newer versions=
 of components below.</p>
